description: This package contains a subset of binaries for the Visual Studio Test Platform (vstest). vstest provides a modern, cross platform testing engine that also powers the testing on .NET Core. Supports the following popular test frameworks - MSTest V2, xUnit and Nunit with support for extensibility. Visit https://github.com/microsoft/vstest to know more about vstest platform. If you need to support legacy test execution via TMI or tests based on [MSTest V1, Ordered, Generic, Web, Cuit], please use Microsoft.TestPlatform package.
title: Microsoft.TestPlatform.Portable
